WarPreppers: ObamaCare

The White House held a secret conference of 10 wealthy donors to plan for a worst-case scenario: a second American revolution that could put armed militants in power. The scenario was reported in leaked transcripts of speeches by President Obama’s top campaign strategist, David Plouffe, and White House Senior Advisor David Axelrod. We’ll speak to John Nichols, the Washington D.C. correspondent of The Nation magazine, who broke the story in a back-to-back interview with Salon.com.
